  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/11d88248c01b47fe8776394e19af1bc5.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><br><i>Take on the role of manager of a single-seater team. Experience race weekends and manage your venue and staff.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your team</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Choose your avatar<br></li><li> Choose your car colors and team name</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/73286350e0f861a87473a1bc3ef28f17.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your pilots and employees</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Select your 3 pilots (2 pilots for the race and a third for research)<br></li><li> Choose your engineers, researchers and marketers to successfully develop your team.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/e658e9ede83faa77cdb08a8b18d26892.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grow your team</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Manage your searches by priority<br></li><li> Improve your infrastructure<br></li><li> Choose your contract<br></li><li> Manage your pilots and staff</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/f2ef0e1d9086ae2e1d330fa55c8bd04e.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take part in race weekends</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Take part in the free practice session to get the best settings for the track<br></li><li> Try to get pole position<br></li><li> Participate in the race with the best strategy</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/e6b0c2d6844f39a243d5512593107248.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/f151756c377c82e6bca773f71384ef08.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game offers:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 27 circuits in the different capitals (and Africa is not forgotten)<br></li><li> 10 AI teams generated procedurally at the start of the season.<br></li><li> Scalable AI. The AI will make its own choices and its own investments.<br></li><li> Scalable weather, depending on the region of the globe.<br></li><li> Procedurally generated drivers/engineers/mechanic/motors/battery pack.<br></li><li> Multiple customization possibilities<br></li><li> Management of the research, marketing and employee team</li></ul></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/11d88248c01b47fe8776394e19af1bc5.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><br><i>Take on the role of manager of a single-seater team. Experience race weekends and manage your venue and staff.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your team</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Choose your avatar<br></li><li> Choose your car colors and team name</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/73286350e0f861a87473a1bc3ef28f17.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your pilots and employees</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Select your 3 pilots (2 pilots for the race and a third for research)<br></li><li> Choose your engineers, researchers and marketers to successfully develop your team.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/e658e9ede83faa77cdb08a8b18d26892.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grow your team</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Manage your searches by priority<br></li><li> Improve your infrastructure<br></li><li> Choose your contract<br></li><li> Manage your pilots and staff</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/f2ef0e1d9086ae2e1d330fa55c8bd04e.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take part in race weekends</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Take part in the free practice session to get the best settings for the track<br></li><li> Try to get pole position<br></li><li> Participate in the race with the best strategy</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/e6b0c2d6844f39a243d5512593107248.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578340/extras/f151756c377c82e6bca773f71384ef08.avif?t=1713863962\" width=560 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game offers:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 27 circuits in the different capitals (and Africa is not forgotten)<br></li><li> 10 AI teams generated procedurally at the start of the season.<br></li><li> Scalable AI. The AI will make its own choices and its own investments.<br></li><li> Scalable weather, depending on the region of the globe.<br></li><li> Procedurally generated drivers/engineers/mechanic/motors/battery pack.<br></li><li> Multiple customization possibilities<br></li><li> Management of the research, marketing and employee team</li></ul></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2></h2>",
